I have completed the task.

1.  **Reproduced Failures:** Verified 3 assertion failures in `DOMStateBuilderTest` where `ariaSnapshot` was empty or `false`.
2.  **Identified Root Cause:** `DOMState.ariaSnapshot` was returning an empty string when `optimizedDOMTree` was null (which is the case in tests that construct `DOMState` manually from `SerializableDOMTreeNode`).
3.  **Applied Fix:** Updated `DOMState.ariaSnapshot` in `pulsar-core/pulsar-browser/src/main/kotlin/ai/platon/browser4/driver/chrome/dom/model/DomModels.kt` to fallback to `serializableTree.toNanoTreeUnfiltered().ariaSnapshot` if `optimizedDOMTree` is null.
4.  **Verified Fix:** Re-ran `DOMStateBuilderTest` and all 16 tests passed.
